ABOUT US:

Welcome to Likha Beauty Studio - Nail Salon
At Likha Beauty Studio, the art of beauty meets craftsmanship. "Likha" is rooted in a word that signifies creation,
and that's precisely what we do with every nail service we offer. We don't just beautify nails; we transform them into miniature canvases that tell a story - your story.

Situated in the heart of Prince George, our salon is more than just a place to get your nails done. It's an oasis of relaxation, a spot where you can unwind,
indulge, and let your inner beauty shine through. Our seasoned professionals are not just nail technicians; they are artisans dedicated to perfecting their craft
and ensuring that every client leaves with a masterpiece at their fingertips.

Using only the finest materials and innovative techniques, we're committed to staying at the forefront of nail artistry.
From classic manicures to intricate nail designs, our menu of services is curated to cater to every individual's unique style and preference.

Join us and experience a world where creativity flows, beauty is crafted, and every nail tells a tale of elegance.


